 <span data-ttu-id="9d1bd-104">控制<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>，则<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>必须引用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>的<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard>，它控制的<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d1bd-104">To control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls that <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d1bd-105">请参阅[如何： 使用事件触发器来控制情节提要启动之后](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md)有关的示例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d1bd-105">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
